data.description: Beautifully updated throughout, designer fixtures and finishes, new HVAC, plumbing, electrical and more. Sited on a park-like 3/4 acre lot offers privacy and yet convenient to shops, restaurants and a commuter’s dream. All bedrooms on main level, including primary suite w/updated bath, 4th bedroom could be perfect multi-gen space w its own fireplace and private entrance. Bring your vision to use the lower level for recreation, added living space, theatre or whatever your dream home includes. Rare THREE car garage can be great workshop or craft space. Beautiful mature landscape includes hardwoods and fruit trees. This ONE truly has it all.
